"Concise history of western music"

"This second edition offers a media package that includes Web-based listing guides for all 68 works in the ""concise"" recordings, online review materials and electronic quizzes on the music and text. The text provides new illustrations, newly designed timelines and maps and marginal references to the ""Norton Anthology of Western Music"" recordings to help students locate selections on the CDs."
" Âm nhạc phương Tây, Lịch sử âm nhạc"
